TFP: Transparent Forwarding Pointer?

&gt; -----Original Message-----
&gt; From: Holliday, Donald B. (LNG-SHEP) [mailto:dhollida@...]
&gt; Sent: Monday, October 22, 2001 10:31 AM
&gt; To: &#39;junit@yahoogroups.com&#39;
